{
  "text": "This could be avoided by shaping directly the pore structure, as done in other studies [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . However, the theoretical concepts used in [CITATION_3] and [CITATION_4] are more complex than those used in the algorithm developed here, which was studied to simplify the approach to the computational generation of porous media.",
